{"tid":2353053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★HK No IT】衞生署仍靠FAX知公立醫院實施和取消病人隔離令  科技基建落伍。","createTime":"2021-01-04T12:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T10:39:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2d9add3912c8c171550368c7922a47aa12ae0e","tid":2353053,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210104/422823973084991488071246.jpeg/9orVb40ckwaEsUSnLbzztDBGzWBJ433SETF6phExeqY?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210104%2F422823973084991488071246.jpeg%2F9orVb40ckwaEsUSnLbzztDBGzWBJ433SETF6phExeqY%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=4d952d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n衞生署仍靠傳真通知公立醫院實施和取消病人隔離令，而醫生要靠傳真接收病人檢測結果，拖慢工作之餘又易生錯漏。署方必須善用網上平台與各持分者便捷溝通，只保留傳真作後備之用。若然把轉用網上簡報會與傳真疫情資訊兩事並列分析，不難推論衞生署資訊科技基建落伍。<br />\n<br />\n政府在《香港智慧城市藍圖》聲音以「創新科技應對疫情」，向外推出「安心出行」、「居安抗疫」家居檢疫系統、電子化健康申報過程等，對內則整合疫情資訊，製作互動地圖儀表板等，卻鮮有提及改善部門之間通報疫情資訊的流程。就此，政府資訊科技總監辦公室和效率促進辦公室應主動向衞生署建議提升運作效率之道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/569764/%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E8%90%BD%E5%BE%8C-%E8%A1%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%2F569764%2F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25BC%258F%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E8%25A1%259E%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=18a7785d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/569764/%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E8%90%BD%E5%BE%8C-%E8%A1%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB</a>"},{"pid":"c2786eb8306ac2cb50bea7acfed3054c60db26bf","tid":2353053,"uid":19454,"